text: "Wandered to LA" is a song by American rapper and singer Juice Wrld and Canadian singer Justin Bieber. It was released on December 3, 2021, and serves as the second single to the former's fourth studio album, Fighting Demons. The song debuted at number 49 on the Billboard Hot 100. ==References== Category:Pop songs Category:2022 songs Category:Juice Wrld songs Category:Justin Bieber songs
